      "para_id": "Q001006.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Ea-bani , the scribe , child of Pišah-ilum , the governor of Kutha , is your servant ."
    }
